---
---
<section id="como-funciona" class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
        ¿Cómo funciona?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Implementar tu bot es más fácil de lo que crees.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 relative">
      <!-- Connecting line for desktop -->
      <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-12 left-[16%] right-[16%] h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-green-500/30 to-transparent -z-10"></div>

      <div class="relative group">
        <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-2xl text-center hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-gray-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold border-2 border-gray-700 mb-6 group-hover:border-green-500 group-hover:text-green-400 transition-colors relative z-10">
            1
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">El cliente escribe</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">Tu cliente envía un mensaje a tu WhatsApp como lo hace normalmente.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative group">
        <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-2xl text-center hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-gray-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold border-2 border-gray-700 mb-6 group-hover:border-green-500 group-hover:text-green-400 transition-colors relative z-10">
            2
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">El bot responde</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">El sistema analiza el mensaje y responde al instante o muestra el menú de opciones.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative group">
        <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-2xl text-center hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-gray-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold border-2 border-gray-700 mb-6 group-hover:border-green-500 group-hover:text-green-400 transition-colors relative z-10">
            3
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Tú tomas el control</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">Si es necesario, recibes una notificación para intervenir y cerrar la venta.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
